import React, { Fragment } from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Head } from './Components/Head'
import { LeftSide } from './Components/LeftSide'
import { Content } from './Components/Content'

export const App = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route
          path="/"
          element={
            <Fragment>
              <Head />
              <LeftSide />
            </Fragment>
          }
        />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
